                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The shadern exhales a cloud of thick smoke in a @Template[type:burst|distance:10]{10-foot burst} centered on them. The cloud remains in place for [[/br 1d4 #rounds]]{1d4 rounds}. All creatures within the smoke become @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Concealed], and all creatures outside the smoke become concealed to creatures within it. Exhaling ends Death Gasp, as the shadern ceases holding their breath.</p>"
